{"tid":728837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"該男子情緒激動，拿出類似手槍物體。稍後經站長勸喻，他收回手槍物體入袋，離開車站","createTime":"2018-07-04T05:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T12:49:18.000Z","uid":73915,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4a18bf1fd6b6ffbd99c59e7a2863cb74a253c7","tid":728837,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:17:52.000Z","msg":"港鐵發言人稱，今早8時15分，一名男子前往沙田站近連城廣場的客務中心，查詢往連城廣場的方法，並要求職員親自帶路。站長向該男子解釋，職員不能擅自離開崗位；其間該男子情緒激動，拿出類似手槍物體。稍後經站長勸喻，他收回手槍物體入袋，離開車站，車站職員隨即報警，事件交由警方調查。而事件對車站運作沒有影響，無人受傷。至於該男子是否要前往連城廣場9樓的培訓中心，則不得而知。"},{"pid":"9243a056a0f137154be9e6ceb825fcf88dc9eff7","tid":728837,"uid":48859,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"收返埋把槍先"},{"pid":"ee0fa98e1d664c71d95aae3870cfda922d5e85fe","tid":728837,"uid":69909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9243a056a0f137154be9e6ceb825fcf88dc9eff7","tid":728837,"uid":48859,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"收返埋把槍先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05174624f6144e09748278f3396e5aa225dcd683","tid":728837,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9243a056a0f137154be9e6ceb825fcf88dc9eff7","tid":728837,"uid":48859,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"收返埋把槍先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2fff948e59cebce683d7e77bcb12fdb5d286de","tid":728837,"uid":155199,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/04/134939_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F134939_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gi